{
    "VERSE": "72:4",
    "ARABIC": "\u0648\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u06e5 \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0642\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0633\u064e\u0641\u0650\u064a\u0647\u064f\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0671\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0634\u064e\u0637\u064e\u0637\u064b\u0627",
    "ENGLISH": {
        "TRANSLATION_0": "Certainly the foolish among us say preposterous things of God.\n",
        "TRANSLATION_1": "and that \u201cthe foolish among us have been wont to say outrageous things about Allah\u201d;\n",
        "TRANSLATION_2": "The dimwit one (the devil) among us has been telling confused lies about God.\n",
        "TRANSLATION_3": "\u2018And that the fool among us used to utter false exaggerations against Allah.\u2019\n",
        "TRANSLATION_4": "`And that the foolish among us used to utter against Allah that which was an enormity in falsehood.'\n",
        "TRANSLATION_5": "And that the foolish amongst us used to forge extravagant things against Allah:\n",
        "TRANSLATION_6": "The fool among us spoke against God outrage,\n",
        "TRANSLATION_7": "And that the foolish one among us used to speak concerning Allah an atrocious lie.\n",
        "TRANSLATION_8": "And [now we know] that the foolish among us have been saying outrageous things about God.\n",
        "TRANSLATION_9": "And the foolish among us were wont to forge lie against Allah exceedingly.\n",
        "TRANSLATION_10": "The foolish ones among us used to speak atrocious lies concerning Allah.\n",
        "TRANSLATION_11": "There were some foolish ones among us, who used to utter extravagant lies against Allah;\n",
        "TRANSLATION_12": "And that the foolish among us [i.e. Iblis (Satan) or the polytheists amongst the jinns] used to utter against Allah that which was wrong and not right.\n",
        "TRANSLATION_13": "The ignorant fool among us has spoken outrageously against Allah,\n",
        "TRANSLATION_14": "But the fools among us used to say nonsense about God.\n",
        "TRANSLATION_15": "And that our foolish one has been saying about Allah an excessive transgression.\n",
        "TRANSLATION_16": "[72:4] And that the fool among us, the ignorant one among us, used to utter atrocious lies against God, extreme calumny by attributing to Him a spouse and a son.\n",
        "TRANSLATION_17": "(And that the foolish one among us) i.e. the devil (used to speak concerning Allah an atrocious lie.\n"
    },
